-Megingjard.description:
[Assassin Class]
PvP: STR bonus does not apply.
PvM: Assassin Class: [Katar Weapon equipped] CRIT ATK + 15%, [Otherwise] STR + 15

Thief Ring.description:
If user's base STR is 90 or higher: HIT + 10, FLEE + 10
If user's base AGI is 90 or higher: ATK + 10, CRIT + 10

Golden Trickle.description:
Bound to Character
Can be enchanted in El Dicastes

Goddess of Fortune's Cursed Brooch.description: When attacking, adds a 0.5% chance to inflict [Curse] on yourself

Shinobi Sash.description: [Note] Slotted version can only be equipped by Ninja

Ring of Flame Lord.bonus: (function (x,y) { x.str += 2;x.vit += 1;x.atk += 15;x.subElement.fire += 10; x.autospell["Fire Ball"] = { type: "onSkill", rate: 15, skillLv: 1, isOffensive: true, trigger: "First Aid"} });

Ring of Resonance.bonus: (function (x,y) { x.agi += 2;x.vit += 1;x.mdef += 2; x.autospell["Tarot Card of Fate"] = { type: "default", rate: 2, skillLv: 5, isOffensive: false, trigger: ""} });

Cursed Hand.description: When attacking there is a 3% chance to autocast Level 1 Critical Wounds

Angelic Ring.description: When using Heal, Sanctuary or Potion Pitcher there is a chance for 3 seconds that gives you the ability + 20% Heal more

Cursed Star.description:
[Curse] only applies with long range attack.
When equipped, HP -50 every 10 seconds
When unequipped, you will lose 300 HP

Dark Knight Glove A.description: When attacking with an ATK based attack, there's a 1% chance to increase ASPD by 2% for 10 seconds

Ring of Water.description: A mysterious ring that is blessed by the Spirit of Water.

Light of El Dicastes.description:
Bound to Game Account
Can be enchanted in El Dicastes

Dark Knight Glove B.description: Small chance of increasing MHP by 10% for 10 seconds when receiving ATK based damage

Telekinetic Orb.bonus: (function (x,y) { x.int += 3;x.maxSp += 30;x.mdef += 1; x.autospell["Sightrasher"] = { type: "onSkill", rate: 2, skillLv: 2, isOffensive: true, trigger: "Two-Hand Sword Mastery"} });

Bakonawa Agimat Tattoo.description: Agimat Tattoo with a dragon swallowing the moon pattern. It is told that the one who owns this tattoo will possess extreme power.

Bangungot Agimat Tattoo.description: Agimat Tattoo with a plump lady pattern. It is told that the one who owns this tattoo will possess extreme power.

Cat Hand Glove.description: A souvenir from Malangdo, just by equpping it will give you a happy mood.

Buwaya Agimat Tattoo.description: Agimat Tattoo with a huge Alligator pattern. It is told that the one who owns this tattoo will possess extreme power.

Bunch of Carnations.description: A carnation bouquet given as gifts to mothers.

Alchemy Glove.description: Magic gloves made for handling corrosive chemicals, smells a bit like charcoal.
Alchemy Glove.bonus: (function (x,y) { x.int += 1;x.mdef += 2;x.magicElementRate.fire += 10; x.autospell["Fire Bolt"] = { type: "onSkill", rate: 1, skillLv: 5, isOffensive: true, trigger: "Increased HP Recovery"} });

Advanced Safety Ring.description:
Add a 1.5% chance of auto casting level 5 Kyrie Eleison when being attacked physically
Every 30 base VIT reduces DEF by 1

[If 2 Advanced Safety Rings are worn together]
Kyrie Eleison level increases to 10 and auto cast chance increases to 2.5%

Pendant Of Guardian.description:
A pendant with black wings. It possesses mysterious power.

Allows the user to use the skill [Call of Guardian].

Silversmith Bracelet.bonus: (function (x,y) { x.mdef += 3; x.enableSkill["Spell Breaker"] = { skillLv: 1, isOffensive: false} });

Thief Handcuff.description: These are handcuffs used only on special occasions to hold the strongest troublemakers when held or transferred from one location to another.

Ring of Fire.description: A mysterious ring that is blessed by the Spirit of Fire.

Ring of Wind.description: A mysterious ring that is blessed by the Spirit of Wind.

Ring of Earth.description: A mysterious ring that is blessed by the Spirit of Earth.

Gold Emblem.description: An emblem showing off enormous courage.
